data.description:
Welcome to 310 Mohawk Trail. This unique property, previously configured as a duplex, has undergone a thoughtful transformation into a sprawling 2,256 square foot single-family home that promises ample living space and incredible versatility.

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a generously sized living room, perfect for creating cherished memories with family and friends. Additionally, there's a dedicated office space that can cater to your work-from-home needs or serve as a creative hub. With four cozy bedrooms you have plenty of space!

Step outside into the great-sized backyard, offering a blank canvas for your outdoor aspirations. Whether you envision lush gardens, a play area for children, or a tranquil retreat, this backyard is ready to accommodate your dreams.  There are two back patios, one is covered and also has a hot tub ready to help you relax and unwind! 

Now is your chance to make 310 Mohawk Trail your new home. This spacious and versatile property is a perfect opportunity to create your ideal living space. Don't let this unique gem slip away. Schedule a showing today and explore the potential and charm that this home has to offer.
